name: Dave Black
description:
I am real easy person to talk to and a loving and outgoing father. I enjoy playing sax which I do often at my leisure time. I like going to the movies, or watching movies in my room or Cabin, I like swimming, listening to music and dance to any kind of music, I sing, sailing, going bowling and also a good cook. I am a family oriented person, love children and there is more, but it would be better for you to find some things out for yourself
For my partner, she has to be accommodating, supportive, caring, honest with me and friendly. A confident and reliable person with a sense of humor, no fusses, always inviting and charming. No nagging and sad moods, respectable and industrious.
